channel.title: FS UK Axoloti complete with Axocontrol and OLED in custom case
channel.description: Hi everyone, I am parting with my underused Axoloti core, bundled with AxoControl and OLED screen in a custom case, all good to go. [Here is an eBay link](https://www.ebay.co.uk/itm/124933905772), shipping in UK Mainland. Open to offers : )
